{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "e996a259-c343-4d6c-88d2-69d86ce428b7", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e996a259-c343-4d6c-88d2-69d86ce428b7@1.pkg/1772597659080/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597659872", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e996a259-c343-4d6c-88d2-69d86ce428b7@1.pkg/1772597659080/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597659872"}, "identifier": "e996a259-c343-4d6c-88d2-69d86ce428b7", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查民法典的含义和意义</p>\n\n<p>A：错误，奶奶将存款赠予孙女，属于赠与行为，涉及民事财产关系，受民法典合同编等相关规定调整。​</p>\n\n<p>B：错误，哥哥与合作伙伴创办公司，涉及民事主体间的合作经营、权利义务划分等，属于民法典中关于法人、合伙等民事关系的调整范围。​</p>\n\n<p>C：错误，邻居拒不归还走失的宠物狗，涉及物权归属问题，宠物狗属于动产，其返还纠纷受民法典物权编调整。​</p>\n\n<p>D：正确，小区物业组织消防知识讲座，是为了提升业主的安全意识，属于公益性质的宣传活动，不涉及平等主体之间的人身关系或财产关系，不在民法典的调整范围内。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（原创）民法典涉及经济社会生活方方面面，同人民群众生产生活密不可分。以下情景不涉及民法典调整范围的是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）​</p>\n", "title": "（原创）民法典涉及经济社会生活方方面面，同人民群众生产生活密不可分。以下情景不涉及民法典调整范围的是（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/e996a259-c343-4d6c-88d2-69d86ce428b7@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755143983639", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": 